      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "# GenAI Overview\n\nThese panels read gen-ai's own custom OTel metrics (`services/gen-ai/app/llm/invoke.py`), emitted around every LLM call made by any of the 4 LLM-backed endpoints (`/summarize`, `/explain`, `/sentiment`, `/qa`), tagged by `endpoint` and `provider` (`logos`/`ollama`). These are pushed via OTLP, not classic-scraped — for gen-ai's generic HTTP-layer RED metrics (all routes, not just LLM ones), see Service Overview / RED Metrics (classic histogram), filtered to `job=gen-ai`.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.3.3",
      "type": "text"
    },
